{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "她的影子", "storyInfo": "戰勝自己內心深處的恐懼後，葦草成功控制源石技藝治療了同伴。當愛布拉娜發出戰爭的號召時，葦草也對同伴們說出了自己的理想。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想像過一切結束的可能，哪怕德拉克的火永遠無法平息。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想像著盛怒的烈焰從她灼痛的胸口迸發，焚毀她被賦予的外殼與身份，令她從此掙脫自己的枷鎖。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但當她真的去觸摸自己的火焰，想要將其握住的時候，她突然在想，會不會自己從來都沒有控制過它。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做得好，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要我真心地誇讚你，這就夠了嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，你已經準備好了......影子要尋回自己，你想要取代我成為“領袖”？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以給你這個機會。你的下一簇火就能將我燒成灰燼。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要......向我伸出手嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火焰燃燒著，她的影子微微搖動。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但葦草移開了視線。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處剛剛醒來的凱莉在墊著的舊圍裙上慢慢地撐起身體，莫蘭哼著歌幫她清洗傷口。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......姐姐，你為什麼會來這裡？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在這裡的時候，你看到的是什麼？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天夜裡的篝火很明亮。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時，維恩正走來走去祈求新的落腳地好做生意，塞爾蒙給自己的武器纏上更多鐵絲。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家開著玩笑叫她領袖，又認真地說，多謝她把大家領到這裡。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，維多利亞人為蓋爾王授銜，然後才在儀式石陣的上方建起了王城。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那以前......它先是塔拉人棲居的家園。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起很早以前的節日冬夜。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們在壁爐前換上一模一樣的新外套，留下了一張兩人都微笑著的照片。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是令人喜愛的......一小團溫暖的火。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......不。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己是影子，這件事，我不在乎。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不是你的影子。我只是，人們理想中“領袖”的影子。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想要一條逃生的路，想找回自己的生活，而我恰好在那裡，被他們所需要。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，我為什麼要戰勝你呢？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g8_galekingruins_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怕死？請別這麼說，凱莉，怕死也不是一件壞事。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還沒有幫到其他塔拉人，就死在同樣想救塔拉人的深池手裡，多遺憾。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你啊，比以前，能說會道多了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "塔拉流民", "content": "還好，我們還有消炎藥......"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "塔拉流民", "content": "嘶......"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弄疼你了？抱歉......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，葦草，你回來了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們今晚躲在這裡的話，應該不會再遇到那些被源石技藝控制的死者。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你去檢查附近的情況了？那就好。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也希望能多停留一段時間，凱莉的傷......情況很差。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，你的表情......", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呵呵，我還記得，一開始，我們把你當成醫生，後來才知道，我們所有人，都只是負傷的人。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的傷，很嚴重？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是那樣......你的傷是可以痊癒的，不用這麼擔心。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只是，你們害怕我的火嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不會。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是她向眼前受傷的塔拉人伸出手。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德拉克的怒火在她的血液中翻湧。昔日紅龍替他的子民流血，一滴血便燒毀整片原野。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她咽下炙熱的吐息，被抑制的火灼燒著她。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果，這樣能撫平傷痛，她願意忍受。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_field_healfield_loop", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "heal", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "soundvolume", "attributes": {"channel": "heal", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——她的手中並未真的燃起火焰，甚至沒有任何光芒閃過。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是所有人都產生了一種感覺——生命在流淌，輕柔得像清晨裡的第一次睜眼。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你的表情......感覺好受一些了？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊......你啊，葦草，難道你真的是醫生？但是醫生也不是像你這樣辦事的呀。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "content": "......"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "end": "true", "content": "不，只是，這終於是我自己的火焰了。", "joined": "還好，我們還有消炎藥......嘶............不，只是，這終於是我自己的火焰了。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願你今晚能睡個好覺，凱莉。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$stranger_intro", "key": "$stranger_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從未想過，維多利亞軍隊之外的人，也能登上這艘高速戰艦。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為在它降下維多利亞旗幟的時候，你們就該想到這一點。", "name": "深池軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對你沒有敵意，塔拉人，我只是對你們的軍事素養，還有你們那位領袖感到好奇。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不希望公爵難得的客人，只是倚仗了自己的德拉克血統。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的骨子裡充滿對我們的傲慢，維多利亞人。", "name": "深池軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可等她登上台開始演講，你會發現，她才是這艘戰艦上所有勢力的主人。", "name": "深池軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "channel": "wind", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "y": 50.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是不明白，你們到底是不是深池？畢竟，你們穿得不太像深池的人。", "name": "受傷的塔拉人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，不管你們是什麼人，你們從維多利亞人手裡救了我的命，我想跟著你們一起走。", "name": "受傷的塔拉人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉，我們沒有幫到你的同伴。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事......沒事。我要是能去救其他人，就算是把他那份活回來了。", "name": "受傷的塔拉人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，葦草，那些人是不是已經放棄追捕我們了？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，追蹤的隊伍消失得有些突兀，但無論如何，對我們來說是好事。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池的軍隊，應該已經集結完畢。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......塔拉人即將向整個維多利亞，發出自己的聲音。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "zoom", "xpos": 0.8, "ypos": 0.8, "scale": 1.5, "fadetime": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 50.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵們。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$eblana_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所帶領的深池部隊，從維多利亞各地來到這裡，與公爵閣下的軍隊會合，是要共同打響一場事關生存的戰爭。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在今天之前，許多人或許還未聽說過深池的名號，或者不理解我們究竟在為什麼而戰鬥。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的戰爭此時蓄勢待發，不過，我們的鬥爭卻已經在過去十年裡發生許多次了。即使是此時，也有代表塔拉人的部隊正在流血。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人所遭受的，只用虐待一詞來概括，恐怕已經不夠。我看到他們的街道化為灰燼，他們的城市變為廢土。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而所求不過飽腹的塔拉人頂著被處決的風險迎接我們的士兵，將他們的麵包掰給我們一半。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到塔拉人在掙扎著向我們呼救。不過，他們不是苦苦等待了十年，而是等待了數百年。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們懇求自己有力的同胞......也懇求有良知的鄰人，懇求那些不願與殘暴者為伍的維多利亞人。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們懇求我們的正視。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻，我們中的一些人知道自己是塔拉人，而另一些人或許會問，我們究竟將要向誰施以援手？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人，塔拉人。和你在一起待久了，我們都習慣用這個詞了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我其實總是在想你說的話，葦草。你說我之前所在的工廠，缺少防護措施，所以大家都會慢慢感染礦石病，慢慢死掉。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，將塔拉人攆去危險的地方工作的工廠老闆，自己也是塔拉人。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有許多，像你這樣說話完全是標準維多利亞口音的人。他們和我們出生在同一個地方，但最害怕和我們閒談，暴露自己的鄉音......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人到底是什麼？我們要救什麼人？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也想了很久。你想聽我的看法嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，葦草，既然沒那麼急著逃命趕路，我們當然樂意聽你說。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......現在的我也許會說，它是幾百年之後，我們身上的苦難終於得到的一個名字。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去，維多利亞人花了很多年，把塔拉這個名字抹掉了。可是，你們一定也感覺到過，自己是跟一些印象聯繫在一起的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人不叫我們塔拉人，他們說“那些口音粗鄙、沒有教養的鄉巴佬，那些遊手好閒的無賴，那些出身不正的下等人”......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，如許多人經歷過的那樣，他們依據我們的族姓，光明正大地從我們身上奪走更多的財產、封地與權利......甚至我們親眷的性命。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許會有人對我們說，那麼為什麼不放棄你們的語言與傳統呢？為什麼不在節日裡同維多利亞人唱一樣的歌謠呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要人們看不出我們是塔拉人，我們就能與他們得到一樣的對待。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，也會有人說，自己雖然是塔拉人，但也靠著意志與野心得到了財富，接受了足夠的教育而躋身上流社會。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——多麼諷刺，我們必須告別自己的文化，背叛自己的家庭，才能從他們那裡掙得被視作一個普通人的尊嚴。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當中不乏卓有成就的英才，可成就的第一步卻是把自己變成維多利亞人。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威靈頓公爵閣下，您一定比任何人都理解......", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有多少人記得您流淌著塔拉人的血呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，既然維多利亞處心積慮地試圖奪走我們的名字，那他們自己真的已經遺忘了塔拉的存在嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#4$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要真是那樣，為什麼塔拉王朝覆滅兩百年後，我，蓋爾王的後裔，一條倖存的德拉克。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——會看著我的父母被阿斯蘭的刺客暗殺，倒在血泊之中？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們仍在害怕，怕我們想起自己的名字，從而戳穿他們的謊言。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我正是來讓大家重新想起這一切的。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_722_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你是說，很多年前，維多利亞的貴族來到了塔拉，把所有塔拉人都變成了自己的領民？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，史書裡大致告訴了我們這些。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於塔拉的事，有許多是編造出來的，但也有真實的部分。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞強行將塔拉地區的君主分封為蓋爾王，脅迫他冊封許多維多利亞貴族。對塔拉地區的不公待遇，也寫在了明文條例中。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候開始，塔拉人的口音就和他們的身份地位聯繫在了一起。維多利亞人指責塔拉人愚笨、粗鄙、缺乏教育。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但又有誰來教過塔拉人？這幾百年來，從沒有人教過我們。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i07", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "x": 100.0, "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人已經慢慢地從最初那片土地上逃出去了，也許隨著移動城市漂流到了維多利亞各處，但卻從未獲得過與維多利亞人同等的選擇權。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名門宴會與高等學府裡，可曾有我們的位置？我們之中如果有許多遊手好閒的人，難道不是因為維多利亞人奪走了我們工作的權利？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在“塔拉人”一詞消失的漫長歲月裡，我們所承受的不公就是這麼巧妙地隱藏了自己，直到現在，我們終於發現自己被逼上絕路的原因。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是塔拉的歷史，還是後人編出的、尋溯塔拉淵源的傳說，我都知道很多。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i08", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "x": 100.0, "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 100.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真實的不公，虛構的夢想，這些，我都可以講給你們聽。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我不說這些，你們也會想......從過去的生活裡逃出去。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還用說，我們活不下去了嘛！", "name": "塔拉流民"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，所以，就算我們認不出自己是塔拉人，也沒關係。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想，熄火鐘敲響的地方，每個人都需要燒穿黑夜的火。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要對抗的，只是橫加在我們身上的不幸。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "所以，我們不得不為了塔拉人的生存而戰鬥。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 26.0, "delay": 0.12, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼下，我們正停靠在橡林郡，這裡曾有塔拉人的街區，但在一些暴虐之徒燃起的大火中化為灰燼。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們之中有視力足夠優秀的人，或許能看見那邊被天災摧毀的塔拉王城。這些都是塔拉人身上的傷痕。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我們的意圖絕不在於找回舊日的塔拉土地，重建那些歷史的殘骸。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是新的大地上的流浪者，我要帶你們去走的，是建起一個新時代、一種新秩序的道路。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i09", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "imageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "duration": 8.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這艘戰艦的下一次停靠，將會在倫蒂尼姆的港口。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我們不是為爭奪維多利亞的冠冕而去。我們只是為了從維多利亞人那裡換回我們的命運，將它握在自己手中。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們如今已經看得很清楚，這些不幸始於維多利亞對塔拉強加的統治與奴役，那麼，我們該讓維多利亞自己否認過去所作所為的正當性。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場戰爭或許不會止於倫蒂尼姆，不過，我們難道會害怕一場漫長的苦戰嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火已經燃起來了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它將燒盡這片大地上陳舊的秩序，燒盡我們身上腐朽的枷鎖。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在將到來的新秩序裡，我懇請你們所有人。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懇請你們不分塔拉與維多利亞，不分地域與出身，只為那光榮的公正而戰鬥，為前所未有的時代而戰鬥。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到塔拉人與維多利亞人一樣，得以自由地書寫自己的夢想，誰也不能阻攔我們。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i08", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，葦草，我們要與什麼戰鬥呢？“要讓塔拉人活下去”，這種說法有點太模糊了。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......過去，我總是想，生命很脆弱。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這片土地上，有很多東西等著殺死我們。我們所有的努力，只不過是拼命地與死亡搏鬥、抗爭。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，最後沒有人能獲勝。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果太在乎人們的性命，我要怎麼面對無處不在的犧牲，和無法追究的橫死？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，生命的分量，就是很沉。我不能逃避它。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i10", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "x": 50.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "imageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 50.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 8.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不可能戰勝死亡，但我們能夠......我們應該給生命以生活的尊嚴。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想......塔拉人應該，在夜晚有一簇溫暖的火，在唱起歌謠時杯中有酒。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人應該，有一天不用再逃亡，不用與自己的親人和愛人分離。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望，塔拉人有自己平靜生活的家園。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望，這一路上我們告別的所有人，能夠在那裡重逢。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 8.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風吹過蘆葦，沙沙聲中，她感到跳動的火焰帶來的灼痛。"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道，那是平實卻遙遠的夢想，此刻站在這裡的人，或許誰都見不到那一天的到來。"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "reed"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......深池的火會燒向這片土地。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它......一定很殘酷。千千萬萬的生命，都只能成為戰火的燃料。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，就算到了那個時候，生命的重量，也絕不會減輕。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......走吧，我們也在其中。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，昨天我收到了家裡來的信。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都過得還行，活著，也許我們打完仗回去，能看到他們生活得更好一點，哈哈。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭，你又不說話了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我只是在想，生活應該是什麼樣子？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$victorianormal_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那麼，你想唱唱歌嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唱吧，趁著難得的好日子，沒有人追殺我們。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在壁爐的火光旁安睡，夢見蜂蜜、甜酒與濃湯♪"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，葦草，要是我們和深池一起行動，你怎麼辦？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "reed", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然我們想要實現的是同一個關於塔拉人的夢想，我和她就沒有區別。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那一天，我會去見她。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}